Key Match Events: Steph Curry scored a season-high 36 points on 13-of-23 shooting from the field with seven made 3-pointers in 37 minutes.
Curry added seven assists, five rebounds, and a steal in Golden State's 127-116 win over the Thunder.
In the third quarter, Curry scored 17 of his 36 points on 7-of-10 shooting.
In the fourth quarter, Curry made two clutch 3-pointers to secure the win for the Warriors.
